import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import { Route, Switch, withRouter, BrowserRouter as Router } from 'react-router-dom'
import { TransitionGroup, CSSTransition } from 'react-transition-group'

import Ceramics from './components/Ceramics'
import Textiles from './components/Textiles'
import Dyno from './components/Dyno'

const StyledBody = styled.div`
  background-color: black;
  height: 100vh;
`

const Body = (props) => {
  return (
    <StyledBody>
      <Router>

        <TransitionGroup>
          <CSSTransition
            // key={location.key}
            classNames="fade"
            timeout={300}>
            <Switch>
              <Route path='/ceramics' component={ Ceramics } />
              <Route path='/textiles' component={ Textiles } />
              <Route path='/dyno/:text' component={ Dyno } />
            </Switch>
          </CSSTransition>
        </TransitionGroup>
      </Router>

    </StyledBody>
  )
}

export default Body
